DecisionMaker is a web application with technologies:
- Spring
- JPA Eclipselink

Status: prototype

Development tools
------------------------------------
- IDE: Eclipse JEE Kepler
- JPA Eclipselink

How to run the project?
------------------------------------
Step 1) Open the project by Eclipse


Step 2) Start database server
The project uses database configuration at folder "DecisionMaker/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml"

For development, you can use HSQL Server at "DecisionMakerServlet/Deployment/hsqldb/".
Start database by executing script start-dms.bat (for Windows) / start-dms.sh (for Linux) from folder "DecisionMakerServlet\Deployment\hsqldb"

Step 3)
For IE, after login, the browser can display HTTP status 404 with url "http://localhost:8080/decisionmaker/img/fancybox/fancy_shadow_nw.png"
Solving:
On Windows, Create soft link "
From the prompt of folder "..../DecisionMakerServlet/src/main/webapp", execute command:
mklink /D img resources\htmlkickstart\css\img

